itemtext: If your goal was a more satisfying life, what would be your first step towards that goal?
Talk about a time you failed and at least one way this failure changed you for the better.
Talk about a time in your past when you successfully coped with a challenge.
Talk about a negative experience in your past when you were disappointed in yourself, in conflict with someone else, or for some other reason have regrets.
Talk about a time you succeeded and describe the steps you took to make this success a reality.
Talk about an event or experience in your past that was meaningful and helped shape how you became the person that you are.
What is keeping you from pursuing the things you want to pursue in life?
How do you treat yourself when you make mistakes?
Describe a recent activity or hobby that you enjoyed.
To what extent do you feel like your life is moving in the right direction?
Do you feel optimistic about the future? Talk about it.
Talk about whether you feel able to manage difficulties in your life.
Talk about something that usually makes you happy.
Is there a community, online or in person, that you feel you have become a part of?
Describe a time you had a significant life difficulty, and how you reacted to it.
Describe a time when you were very focused on a task.
Describe a time when you talked with another person about their problems.
How would you describe yourself as a person?
Talk about a time when you sacrificed for someone else.
Talk about a time when you felt truly happy and alive.
Describe an event that recently made you upset. What did that feel like for you?
